---
title: "C4 Level 4 — Code: tk-core Memory Management & Lifetime Model"
---
classDiagram
    direction TB

    class SweepArena {
        -inner: Bump  [cpu-only]
        -storage: ArenaStorage  [backend-cuda]
        +new(capacity_bytes) Self
        +alloc_tensor~T~(shape) DenseTensor~'_, T~
        +alloc_slice_zeroed~T~(len) &[T]
        +alloc_slice_uninit~T~(len) &mut [T]
        +reset()
        +allocated_bytes() usize
    }

    class ArenaStorage {
        <<enum — backend-cuda only>>
        Pinned(PinnedArena)
        Pageable(Bump)
    }

    class PinnedArena {
        <<backend-cuda only>>
        -inner: Bump
        -capacity: usize
        +new(capacity_bytes) Result~Self~
        +reset()
        +capacity() usize
        +allocated_bytes() usize
    }

    class PinnedMemoryTracker {
        <<backend-cuda only>>
        -PINNED_BYTES_ALLOCATED: AtomicUsize$
        -PINNED_BYTES_LIMIT: AtomicUsize$
        +initialize_budget(max_bytes)$
        +try_reserve(bytes) bool$
        +release(bytes)$
        +allocated_bytes() usize$
        +budget_limit() usize$
    }

    class Bump {
        <<bumpalo>>
        Bump allocator
    }

    SweepArena *-- Bump : cpu-only
    SweepArena *-- ArenaStorage : backend-cuda
    ArenaStorage *-- PinnedArena
    ArenaStorage *-- Bump
    PinnedArena *-- Bump : wraps (placeholder)
    SweepArena ..> PinnedMemoryTracker : budget check

    class DenseTensor~'a, T~ {
        shape: TensorShape
        storage: TensorStorage~'a, T~
        offset: usize
    }

    class TensorStorage~'a, T~ {
        <<enum>>
        Owned(Vec~T~)
        Borrowed(&'a [T])
    }

    note for SweepArena "alloc_tensor flow:\n1. Bump-allocate zeroed slice\n2. Wrap as TensorStorage::Borrowed\n3. Return DenseTensor with lifetime\n   tied to arena ('a)\n\nNo heap Vec created."

    SweepArena ..> DenseTensor~'a, T~ : allocates (Borrowed)
    DenseTensor~'a, T~ *-- TensorStorage~'a, T~ : owns

    note for TensorStorage~'a, T~ "Copy-on-Write:\n- Arena tensors start as Borrowed\n- into_owned() clones to Owned(Vec)\n- Must call before arena.reset()\n  to persist data"
